<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>国土报最新头条</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Sat, 14 Oct 2023 20:06:28 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>报告：联邦调查局局长警告说，自哈马斯袭击以来，美国“威胁急剧上升”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-14/ty-article/report-fbi-director-warns-that-u-s-sees-sharp-uptick-in-threats-since-hamas-attack/0000018b-2f9e-d450-a3af-6f9e5ed40000</link><description>雷发出警告的一天前，国家安全委员会发言人约翰·柯比表示，美国没有关于哈马斯袭击造成的国内威胁的任何具体情报。</description><pubDate>Sat, 14 Oct 2023 19:30:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-14/ty-article/report-fbi-director-warns-that-u-s-sees-sharp-uptick-in-threats-since-hamas-attack/0000018b-2f9e-d450-a3af-6f9e5ed40000</guid></item><item><title>美国与以色列和中东国家合作解决加沙人道主义危机</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-10-14/ty-article/.premium/u-s-working-with-israel-mideast-nations-to-address-gaza-humanitarian-crisis/0000018b-2ed4-da5e-abef-aff5212d0000</link><description>美国总统乔·拜登表示，埃及、约旦和联合国都参与了这些努力，因为国际组织称加沙局势已接近无可挽回的境地，要求他们提供帮助的压力越来越大。</description><pubDate>Sat, 14 Oct 2023 16:01:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-10-14/ty-article/.premium/u-s-working-with-israel-mideast-nations-to-address-gaza-humanitarian-crisis/0000018b-2ed4-da5e-abef-aff5212d0000</guid></item><item><title>好莱坞谴责哈马斯袭击，迪士尼承诺提供 200 万美元用于以色列救援</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-10-14/ty-article/.premium/hollywood-condemn-hamas-attacks-disney-pledges-2-million-for-relief-in-israel/0000018b-2ea4-dff1-a5eb-fefd9a320000</link><description>一封由 700 名演员、电影制片人和其他人签署的信敦促娱乐业的其他成员公开反对袭击并要求释放哈马斯劫持的人质</description><pubDate>Sat, 14 Oct 2023 15:19:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-10-14/ty-article/.premium/hollywood-condemn-hamas-attacks-disney-pledges-2-million-for-relief-in-israel/0000018b-2ea4-dff1-a5eb-fefd9a320000</guid></item><item><title>中东和西方国家爆发支持以色列和巴勒斯坦的抗议活动</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/2023-10-14/ty-article/protests-to-support-israel-palestinians-erupt-across-middle-east-western-countries/0000018b-2e0d-d1bc-a58b-6faf75b70000</link><description>哈马斯袭击后，美国、法国和其他地方的犹太社区举行集会声援以色列，中东以及亚洲、欧洲和美国部分地区的抗议者聚集在一起支持巴勒斯坦人</description><pubDate>Sat, 14 Oct 2023 13:13:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/2023-10-14/ty-article/protests-to-support-israel-palestinians-erupt-across-middle-east-western-countries/0000018b-2e0d-d1bc-a58b-6faf75b70000</guid></item><item><title>一名疑似伊斯兰极端分子持刀刺死法国后，法国部署7000名士兵</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/europe/2023-10-14/ty-article/france-is-deploying-7-000-troops-after-a-deadly-stabbing-by-a-suspected-islamic-radical/0000018b-2de9-dff1-a5eb-fffd05330000</link><description>此外，巴黎卢浮宫博物馆正在疏散所有游客和工作人员，并因收到书面威胁而于周六早些时候闭馆。据称，这一举措与政府在学校发生疑似极端分子持刀伤人致死事件后决定让法国进入高度戒备状态有关。</description><pubDate>Sat, 14 Oct 2023 11:50:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/europe/2023-10-14/ty-article/france-is-deploying-7-000-troops-after-a-deadly-stabbing-by-a-suspected-islamic-radical/0000018b-2de9-dff1-a5eb-fffd05330000</guid></item><item><title>从致命袭击中检索到的文件显示，哈马斯计划杀害和绑架平民</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-14/ty-article/hamas-planned-to-kill-and-abduct-civilians-documents-from-the-deadly-assault-reveal/0000018b-2d74-dff1-a5eb-fffde4b70000</link><description>缴获的文件显示，哈马斯对以色列边境社区的屠杀是经过精心策划的，最初的目的是伤害包括儿童在内的平民。该恐怖组织试图声称绑架人员不是此次袭击的官方目标</description><pubDate>Sat, 14 Oct 2023 10:34:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-14/ty-article/hamas-planned-to-kill-and-abduct-civilians-documents-from-the-deadly-assault-reveal/0000018b-2d74-dff1-a5eb-fffde4b70000</guid></item><item><title>被关押在加沙的以色列人家属感到愤怒和焦虑，要求国际社会提供支持</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-14/ty-article-magazine/.premium/angry-and-anxious-families-of-israelis-held-in-gaza-demand-international-support/0000018b-2d07-da5e-abef-ad6744130000</link><description>哈马斯突然袭击后，迫切需要有关失踪亲人、被扣为人质或仍下落不明的以色列人家人的信息，这对政府呼吁保持耐心的呼吁感到愤怒</description><pubDate>Sat, 14 Oct 2023 08:27:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-14/ty-article-magazine/.premium/angry-and-anxious-families-of-israelis-held-in-gaza-demand-international-support/0000018b-2d07-da5e-abef-ad6744130000</guid></item><item><title>给内塔尼亚胡彻底搞砸的政府的最佳建议</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-10-14/ty-article-opinion/.premium/the-best-advice-for-netanyahus-fully-screw-up-government/0000018b-2a34-d628-a3af-febddbd20000</link><description></description><pubDate>Sat, 14 Oct 2023 06:16:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-10-14/ty-article-opinion/.premium/the-best-advice-for-netanyahus-fully-screw-up-government/0000018b-2a34-d628-a3af-febddbd20000</guid></item><item><title>以色列军队在来自黎巴嫩加沙的火箭弹袭击中准备对加沙进行地面入侵</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-14/ty-article-live/idf-kills-hamas-head-of-aerial-forces-strikes-dozens-of-gaza-targets-overnight/0000018b-2c64-da5e-abef-ad656b090000</link><description>以色列和加沙的战争进入第八天，已有 1,200 多名以色列人死亡，其中大部分是哈马斯上周六对加沙边境社区发动的致命袭击造成的。周六，至少有 13 名以色列人在加沙和黎巴嫩附近受伤 ■ 加沙死亡人数达到 2,215 ■ 以色列国防军称击毙了哈马斯指挥官，他是大屠杀的领导者 ■ 以色列军队在加沙的一次明显的首次地面行动中打捞了一些以色列人质的尸体入侵加沙地带 ■ 以色列国防军袭击哈马斯基础设施，敦促数千巴勒斯坦人向南逃亡</description><pubDate>Sat, 14 Oct 2023 05:35:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-14/ty-article-live/idf-kills-hamas-head-of-aerial-forces-strikes-dozens-of-gaza-targets-overnight/0000018b-2c64-da5e-abef-ad656b090000</guid></item><item><title>以色列军队袭击加沙地带并打捞失踪以色列人的尸体</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-14/ty-article/.premium/israeli-army-raids-gaza-strip-retrieves-bodies-of-missing-israelis/0000018b-2bc6-dff1-a5eb-ffff1b670000</link><description>以色列证实地面部队已进入加沙地带，“摧毁了恐怖分子小队和基础设施”，并发现了可能导致更多人员失踪的物品</description><pubDate>Sat, 14 Oct 2023 01:45:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-14/ty-article/.premium/israeli-army-raids-gaza-strip-retrieves-bodies-of-missing-israelis/0000018b-2bc6-dff1-a5eb-ffff1b670000</guid></item><item><title>哈马斯袭击后对以色列南部的一次令人毛骨悚然的访问唤起了伊斯兰国和乌克兰</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-14/ty-article-magazine/.premium/a-bloodcurdling-visit-to-israels-south-after-the-hamas-attack-evokes-isis-and-ukraine/0000018b-2b0a-d1bc-a58b-6bafb8550000</link><description>本周，斯德洛特和附近其他城镇的街道空无一人，但烧毁的汽车和血迹仍然可见，枪战的声音清晰可闻。以色列从未发生过这样的事情</description><pubDate>Fri, 13 Oct 2023 23:24:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-14/ty-article-magazine/.premium/a-bloodcurdling-visit-to-israels-south-after-the-hamas-attack-evokes-isis-and-ukraine/0000018b-2b0a-d1bc-a58b-6bafb8550000</guid></item><item><title>“哈马斯的袭击是内部人员所为”：为什么疯狂的阴谋论如此流行？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-14/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/hamas-attack-was-an-inside-job-why-are-wild-conspiracy-theories-so-popular/0000018b-2a03-dff1-a5eb-fefff50d0000</link><description>一些以色列右翼人士将加沙战争归咎于以色列国防军高层或反政府抗议者。从比比主义者到特朗普，研究为寻找“内部叛徒”提供了一些线索</description><pubDate>Fri, 13 Oct 2023 21:51:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-14/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/hamas-attack-was-an-inside-job-why-are-wild-conspiracy-theories-so-popular/0000018b-2a03-dff1-a5eb-fefff50d0000</guid></item><item><title>巴勒斯坦卫生部称，两名巴勒斯坦人在定居者袭击救护车中丧生</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-14/ty-article/.premium/two-palestinians-killed-in-settler-attack-on-ambulances-palestinian-health-ministry-says/0000018b-2550-d680-af9b-27dec5a90000</link><description>以色列军队参加了部分预先安排的袭击，目前尚不清楚是谁射杀了两名巴勒斯坦人——一对父子——。袭击的救护车载着在附近村庄被杀的巴勒斯坦人的尸体，该地区有武装定居者的记录</description><pubDate>Fri, 13 Oct 2023 21:41:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-14/ty-article/.premium/two-palestinians-killed-in-settler-attack-on-ambulances-palestinian-health-ministry-says/0000018b-2550-d680-af9b-27dec5a90000</guid></item><item><title>“完全是假的”：以色列国家安全顾问否认收到埃及关于哈马斯袭击的警告</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-13/ty-article/.premium/israels-national-security-adviser-denies-receiving-egyptian-warning-of-hamas-attack/0000018b-28c9-d1bc-a58b-69ef2ed70000</link><description>国家安全顾问查奇·哈内格比表示，在美国议员告诉记者“埃及三天前已警告以色列人”后，以色列收到了有关哈马斯袭击的“零信息”</description><pubDate>Fri, 13 Oct 2023 19:22:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-13/ty-article/.premium/israels-national-security-adviser-denies-receiving-egyptian-warning-of-hamas-attack/0000018b-28c9-d1bc-a58b-69ef2ed70000</guid></item><item><title>“这关乎犹太人的存在”：以色列与哈马斯的战争蔓延到哥伦比亚大学校园</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-10-13/ty-article/.premium/this-is-about-jewish-existence-israel-hamas-war-spills-into-columbia-campus/0000018b-29f2-dff1-a5eb-ffffdfec0000</link><description>校园里有自越南战争以来最大规模的警察包围，支持巴勒斯坦的学生聚集在哥伦比亚大学，当一位发言者将以色列公民的屠杀描述为“对定居者殖民压迫者的反攻”时，他们欢呼起来</description><pubDate>Fri, 13 Oct 2023 17:55:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-10-13/ty-article/.premium/this-is-about-jewish-existence-israel-hamas-war-spills-into-columbia-campus/0000018b-29f2-dff1-a5eb-ffffdfec0000</guid></item><item><title>报道：由于与哈马斯的持续战争，沙特阿拉伯冻结了与以色列的正常化谈判</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-13/ty-article/.premium/saudi-arabia-freezes-normalization-talks-with-israel-amid-ongoing-war-with-hamas/0000018b-2a0b-d1bc-a58b-6baf83c20000</link><description>这场冲突还促使沙特与伊朗接触。沙特王储穆罕默德·本·萨勒曼接到伊朗总统易卜拉欣·莱西打来的第一个电话，此时利雅得正试图阻止该地区更广泛的暴力事件激增</description><pubDate>Fri, 13 Oct 2023 17:52:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-13/ty-article/.premium/saudi-arabia-freezes-normalization-talks-with-israel-amid-ongoing-war-with-hamas/0000018b-2a0b-d1bc-a58b-6baf83c20000</guid></item><item><title>进步人士警告以色列在加沙进行“种族清洗”，与主流民主党的分歧扩大</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-10-13/ty-article/.premium/progressives-warn-of-ethnic-cleansing-in-gaza-widening-rift-with-mainstream-dems/0000018b-29b4-dff1-a5eb-fffdfc710000</link><description>这些言论发表之际，进步人士与其同事之间的分歧日益扩大，他们谴责他们最初的回应不够充分，并提供了虚假的对等内容</description><pubDate>Fri, 13 Oct 2023 15:58:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-10-13/ty-article/.premium/progressives-warn-of-ethnic-cleansing-in-gaza-widening-rift-with-mainstream-dems/0000018b-29b4-dff1-a5eb-fffdfc710000</guid></item><item><title>布林肯告诉阿巴斯，约旦国王阿卜杜拉：哈马斯不代表巴勒斯坦人</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-10-13/ty-article/.premium/blinken-tells-abbas-jordans-king-abdullah-hamas-doesnt-stand-for-palestinians/0000018b-2950-d628-a3af-fdd9de9e0000</link><description>在与阿卜杜拉会面期间，他们讨论了确保人质获释的努力、防止冲突扩大的重要性以及加沙平民的人道主义需求</description><pubDate>Fri, 13 Oct 2023 14:41:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-10-13/ty-article/.premium/blinken-tells-abbas-jordans-king-abdullah-hamas-doesnt-stand-for-palestinians/0000018b-2950-d628-a3af-fdd9de9e0000</guid></item><item><title>不方便的背景：巴勒斯坦人因为犹太人而屠杀犹太人</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-13/ty-article-opinion/.premium/the-inconvenient-context-palestinians-massacred-jews-for-being-jews/0000018b-2890-dff1-a5eb-fefd6e7d0000</link><description>坚持认为加沙周边以色列社区 1,300 多人被谋杀只是有政治背景，就是故意忽视哈马斯、真主党、法国和巴基斯坦伊斯兰主义者谋杀犹太人与匹兹堡枪击案之间的联系</description><pubDate>Fri, 13 Oct 2023 13:07:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-13/ty-article-opinion/.premium/the-inconvenient-context-palestinians-massacred-jews-for-being-jews/0000018b-2890-dff1-a5eb-fefd6e7d0000</guid></item><item><title>布鲁克林篮网队与拉阿纳纳马卡比队的 NBA 季前赛变成了对以色列的支持</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/sports/2023-10-13/ty-article/.premium/brooklyn-nets-maccabi-raanana-pre-season-game-turns-into-show-of-support-for-israel/0000018b-2889-d450-a3af-699d1ed60000</link><description>在哈马斯周六对以色列平民进行屠杀之后，与以色列有关的一切都不再一样了——包括周四以色列球队与美国 NBA 对手之间的例行篮球比赛</description><pubDate>Fri, 13 Oct 2023 12:41:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/sports/2023-10-13/ty-article/.premium/brooklyn-nets-maccabi-raanana-pre-season-game-turns-into-show-of-support-for-israel/0000018b-2889-d450-a3af-699d1ed60000</guid></item></channel></rss>